data.description: As you step inside, you'll notice the care and attention to detail that has gone into making this immaculate house a home. In addition to the 3 bedrooms, including a spacious first-floor primary suite, and 2.5 bathrooms, the heart of this home is its fully updated kitchen, featuring beautiful granite countertops and newer appliances. The upgraded primary bathroom is a true oasis, boasting a separate shower and a luxurious jetted tub – perfect for unwinding after a long day. Plus, the walk-in closet provides ample space for all your wardrobe needs. The newer flooring and gorgeous brick fireplace are extras that tie everything together. One of the standout features of this property is its HUGE backyard. Whether you're hosting BBQs or just relaxing in the open air, this outdoor space is truly incredible. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a beautifully updated, move-in ready home. Your dream home awaits!
